{"tid":856256,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟依家仲有乜野係制衡到政府？","createTime":"2018-10-10T13:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T16:29:14.000Z","uid":36470,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c83aa16651245c54d93d5cf8f9666887c8d2291b","tid":856256,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:19:51.000Z","msg":"立法機關己經失效，香港冇晒儲備真係陷港產都似<br />\n<br />\n1 醫療社福運作唔到<br />\n2 再有一個索羅斯出現，香港維繫唔到聯繫匯率，隨便一個富豪都可以打沉香港<br />\n3 外匯《50%既國家唔可以印銀紙＝唔可以有自己貨幣<br />\n4 港紙＝廢票？<br />\n5 會否慘過三年零八個月既日治時期<br />\n<br />\n睇埋D留言仲眼火爆<br />\n（繼續交稅啦香港人）<br />\n（聽日準時番工做港豬）<br />\n（關我咩事，D福利我有份用架？）<br />\n（咪咁天真，接受現實啦）<br />\n<br />\n香港人仲係一盆散沙咁，自己人打自己人<br />\n<br />\n再咁落去，香港人同猶太人既下場冇分別<br />\n<br />\n要接受現實，所以大家真係諗住坐係到等死？<br />\n<br />\n定係有辦法引起國際關注？ 一萬億送比美國送埋塊地比佢都冇咁嬲<br />\n<br />\n香港人，醒未？"},{"pid":"b785a3b71f2d7d0153dc65eb9164993e2a2da636","tid":856256,"uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:24:47.000Z","msg":"醒都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可以點"},{"pid":"e1fb36dc6076e09addfb4e4952c9a9ffccf1c6e9","tid":856256,"uid":178574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"醒左可以點"},{"pid":"55af8635ea884370fd999f8907594653c35d0732","tid":856256,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:29:31.000Z","msg":"？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7fed40ab98ec11c891deb4c8a2afebe252a5ee","tid":856256,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:29:35.000Z","msg":"美國白宮"},{"pid":"bcef160cb4b84588b1dd55e0dad98ee3b6efe193","tid":856256,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:30:36.000Z","msg":"我之前OT開2 3個鐘<br />\n<br />\n我覺得今日起每人OT少10-15分鐘就可以制衡到商家同政府<br />\n<br />\n<img 